com.i2group.apollo.model.schema.transport

Class ProhibitedCreate

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.i2group.apollo.model.schema.transport.ProhibitedOperation
      • com.i2group.apollo.model.schema.transport.ProhibitedCreate

  • public final class ProhibitedCreate
extends ProhibitedOperation
    A ProhibitedOperation that indicates that users cannot create items, property groups, or properties of a particular type.

    When a type has this indicator set in the Schema, a service that stores data must block any request from a client to introduce new data of that type.

    Since:
    5.0
